This project which contains 2 files named Covid Deaths and Covid Vaccinations, which are both
loaded on SSMS . Data types of relevant field were changed to integer to avoid later conversion
during code execution.
The aim of this Project is to analyse the dataset related to deaths and vaccinations due to Covid-19.
Initially, Total deaths were analysed grouped by Location.
Then total deaths were analysed by continents using the syntax below.
Next the global deaths percentage was queried
Using the Syntax below, Percentage of population was analysed who received atleast one
Covid Vaccination and this was accomplished by joining two tables covid deaths and covid
vaccinations
Furthermore, analysing the mortality rate using new deaths vs population was carried out using CTE
Temp table was created
Finally to store the data for later visualisation, Create view was created
